Topics: ExpandoMetaClass, method injection
Question:
How would you add a new method greet to all Strings in Groovy?

A) String.metaClass.greet = { -> "Hi $delegate" } 

B) String.addMethod("greet")

C) def greet(String s) { ... }

D) String.newMethod("greet")

Answer: A) String.metaClass.greet = { -> "Hi $delegate" }
